    "body": "I reworked this section, sticking to the semantics and leaving out misleading implementation\ndetails.  I avoid mentioning the stack and heap entirely, motivating more idomatic use of boxes\nwith a simple linked list.  For Rc, I removed type parameters entirely, since they don't add anything; I clarified the difference between references and owners, and the use of Arc with multiple threads.\n\nThanks for the input; it helped clarify my understanding and make the Guide simpler and more accurate.  Let me know if you have any more feedback.\n",
